org.eclipse.gmt.modisco.java.cdo.meta
Interface JavaPackage

All Superinterfaces:
JavaPackage
public interface JavaPackage
extends JavaPackage

The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type

See Also:
